{"tid":1396890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔明點解罷工要老細批","createTime":"2019-08-02T08:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T16:42:10.000Z","uid":14503,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"899460c0afcb258ed364861be9a09a4a0ac4cf4d","tid":1396890,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"正如圍狗籠要同狗隻申請不反對通知書一樣<br />\n仲要罷工唔係犯法<br />\n好啦, 而家D發鈔銀行開始話8月5唔比請假, D人又真係驚唔夠膽請...<br />\n喂喂等陣先....你依家係罷工wo.......<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">基本法第二十七條訂明香港居民享有「組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由」。本港並無法例禁止罷工，僱員有參加工會和罷工的自由和權利。</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/199901/20/0120smec.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F199901%2F20%2F0120smec.htm&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjFgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=bc9f1ab4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/199901/20/0120smec.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d4adcbaa0fa227357269121fca931107bf5e5ab1","tid":1396890,"uid":259613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HpxenzJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHpxenzJ.jpg&h=8c914f46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33bfa3f5c9c3980fc38becc4ce5ca8670e05d18b","tid":1396890,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:55:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97b27084dbbb2ac9c806675bdcfe16b44d8d233e","tid":1396890,"uid":126226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:04:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef7837581b34f6a0cf0bfa1902fecee05243ed93","tid":1396890,"uid":90692,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"因為要有工會。"},{"pid":"f0e553e71b49d17ef877e34f74e19993ffa33865","tid":1396890,"uid":14503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ef7837581b34f6a0cf0bfa1902fecee05243ed93","tid":1396