\n屌你老味而家好心同你請個假，公司仲撚夠膽兇返人轉頭？"},{"pid":"41b6802ddafb110324b07ac3f1f9448798b87017","tid":1396890,"uid":168911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"唔理啦，唔好批鬥呢d野<br />\n請假又好，no show又好<br />\n總之個效果係唔返工去集會"},{"pid":"c700ed61b03091cef06bef96068ae7779a060794","tid":1396890,"uid":38438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4adcbaa0fa227357269121fca931107bf5e5ab1","tid":1396890,"uid":259613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HpxenzJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHpxenzJ.jpg&h=8c914f46&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:17:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"87432232ac8497fdb0f6cf36641be6379b348596","tid":1396890,"uid":14503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41b6802ddafb110324b07ac3f1f9448798b87017","tid":1396890,"uid":168911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"唔理啦，唔好批鬥呢d野<br />\n請假又好，no show又好<br />\n總之個效果係唔返工去集會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:19:34.000Z","msg":"唔係批鬥, 係想叫人明白罷工意義, 唔應該因為公司比壓力而唔做, 運動係會預左有某程度上既犧牲"},{"pid":"a4d48da120c709ba72ef9ef7b03a2eeee221e55a","tid":1396890,"uid":24265,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:20:34.000Z","msg":"因為你食屋企住屋企無負擔<br />\n<br />\n幾多人要供養父母 供樓 供書教學<br />\n<br />\n唔好ff咁撚多老細唔會/唔可以抽後帳啦"},{"pid":"b5e85d55ec822af1ecce150113204c98c8d634a1","tid":1396890,"uid":67197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34e454b8c8883ba8bcb51821c826fb58c5af73a","tid":1396890,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4d48da120c709ba72ef9ef7b03a2eeee221e55a","tid":1396890,"uid":24265,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:20:34.000Z","msg":"因為你食屋企住屋企無負擔<br />\n<br />\n幾多人要供養父母 供樓 供書